ing her ordeal, she said that the 36-year-old actress had given her alcohol and asked her in a dare to give Mr Marke oral sex. After that, she told the police that Mr Marke had sex with both of them. She said to the police, “I knew it was wrong but I just didn’t know how to get out of the situation or say anything. I remember trying to copy Zara’s reaction at the time because I looked up to her and tried to be like her in every way.” The victim said no one would believe her and that she was threatened by Mr Marke if she told anyone about it. “He just said nobody would believe me if I told them anyway.” The couple would have been 20 or 21 and 42 or 43 years old when the alleged abuse started. Additional reports from the police state that the couple at the time were both martial arts instructors. Mr Marke also faces four other charges of child abuse which another woman reported to the police.
She was aged 15 when she was allegedly abused by him between 2002 and 2003.